<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>ActiveRabbit – Quota Exceeded</title>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 24px 20px;
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 24px 0 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .button-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0 8px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background: #667eea;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;">
          <%= image_tag "faviicons/favicon-512.png",
            width: 48,
            height: 48,
            style: "display:block;margin-right:16px;" %>

          <div style="text-align:left;">
            <div style="font-weight:700;font-size:16px;line-height:1.25;">
              <%= @resource_name %> Quota Exceeded
            </div>
            <div style="font-size:13px;opacity:0.9;margin-top:2px;">
              ActiveRabbit Quota Alert
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2>Quota Exceeded</h2>

      <p>
        You have reached <strong><%= @percentage.round %>%</strong> of your monthly quota for the team <strong><%= @account.name %></strong>. Upgrade your plan to increase your limits and continue using all features.
      </p>

      <div class="button-wrapper">
        <a href="<%= @upgrade_url %>" class="button">Upgrade Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      ActiveRabbit – AI-Powered Error Tracking for Rails
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
